{"type":"click","text":"C\n    \n      Dashboard home widget + dedicated page\n      Add a small \"This month's spend\" card to the dashboard home (alongside Sites, Personas, Articles), and clicking it opens a full /dashboard/usage page with all the detail.\n      \n        Pros\n          Spending visible at a glance on home\n          Full detail available one click away\n          Budget warning visible without navigating\n        \n        Cons\n          Two places to build (widget + full page)\n          Slightly more work","choice":"c","id":null,"timestamp":1773404839710}
